OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780423900
OL,3,CGroup condemns calls for 'vigilante
OL,4,Cjustice' against police over Nowak case
OL,6,FA policing group has condemned calls
OL,7,Ffor "vigilante justice" against
OL,8,Fofficers over the Henry Nowak case,
OL,9,Fwith some wrongly identified on social
OL,10,Fmedia as having been involved.
OL,12,FHampshire Police Federation said some
OL,13,Fofficers had personal details such as
OL,14,Ftheir home addresses published, and
OL,15,Fcalled on politicians and social media
OL,16,Ffigures to be more responsible in what
OL,17,Fthey say.
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@WO]
