OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780423900
OL,3,CGroup condemns calls for 'vigilante
OL,4,Cjustice' against police over Nowak case
OL,6,FHenry Nowak, 18, was handcuffed by
OL,7,FHampshire police officers as he lay
OL,8,Fdying from stab wounds in Southampton
OL,9,Fin December after his killer lied that
OL,10,Fhe was drunk and had launched a racist
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FBody-worn footage has been released by
OL,14,Fthe force in which Henry can be heard
OL,15,Ftelling them that he has been stabbed,
OL,16,Fbut he is ignored.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780423900
OL,3,CGroup condemns calls for 'vigilante
OL,4,Cjustice' against police over Nowak case
OL,6,FWatchdog the Independent Office for
OL,7,FPolice Conduct (IOPC) is investigating
OL,8,Fthe handling of the case, but has said
OL,9,Fthat officers are being treated as
OL,10,Fwitnesses at this stage.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Hampshire Police
OL,13,FFederation said: "The murder of Henry
OL,14,FNowak was a tragedy, our thoughts are
OL,15,Fwith his family and friends.
OL,17,F"The officers' actions that night are
OL,18,Fsubject to rigorous independent
OL,19,Fscrutiny and we must let that process
OL,20,Frun its course.
OL,26,@uD@ROUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780423900
OL,3,CGroup condemns calls for 'vigilante
OL,4,Cjustice' against police over Nowak case
OL,6,F"The Police Federation condemns in the
OL,7,Fstrongest possible terms the calls for
OL,8,Fmob or vigilante justice against
OL,9,Fofficers we have seen in recent days.
OL,11,F"That has included police officers
OL,12,Fbeing wrongly identified as being
OL,13,Finvolved in the incident and personal
OL,14,Fdetails such as home address being
OL,15,Fwidely published.
OL,17,F"We call on politicians of all parties
OL,18,Fand media commentators to be more
OL,19,Fresponsible in their comments ` and
OL,20,Fallow due process for the officers
OL,21,Finvolved to ensue.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780423900
OL,3,CGroup condemns calls for 'vigilante
OL,4,Cjustice' against police over Nowak case
OL,6,F"As a staff association we are
OL,7,Fsupporting all Hampshire Police
OL,8,Fofficers and we urge all our members
OL,9,Fto take appropriate action online and
OL,10,Foffline to stay safe."
OL,12,FInvestigators from the IOPC said they
OL,13,Fwill meet Mr Nowak's family and keep
OL,14,Fthem updated with their investigation.
OL,16,FThey are examining a large amount of
OL,17,Fbody-worn video as well as material
OL,18,Fpresented during the trial of murderer
OL,19,FVickrum Digwa.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
