OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780423900
OL,3,CGroup condemns calls for 'vigilante
OL,4,Cjustice' against police over Nowak case
OL,6,FIOPC director Derrick Campbell said:
OL,7,F"We acknowledge that this case has
OL,8,Fraised questions about the actions of
OL,9,Fthe attending officers and we are
OL,10,Faware that a few minutes of police
OL,11,Fbody-worn footage has been issued by
OL,12,Fthe force following the conclusion of
OL,13,Fcriminal proceedings.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780423900
OL,3,CGroup condemns calls for 'vigilante
OL,4,Cjustice' against police over Nowak case
OL,6,F"As part of our ongoing investigation
OL,7,Fwe are reviewing a large amount of
OL,8,Fpolice body-worn footage, which we
OL,9,Fneed to consider in context with other
OL,10,Fevidence we have obtained, including
OL,11,Freviewing material presented during
OL,12,Fthe murder trial, as we establish the
OL,13,Ffull circumstances.
OL,15,F"Now that criminal proceedings have
OL,16,Fconcluded, we are planning to meet
OL,17,Fwith Mr Nowak's family and provide
OL,18,Fthem with updates about our
OL,19,Finvestigation."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU{D@OO]
